{"word":"G2897 - κραιπάλη - kraipálē - krahee-pal'-ay - Surfeiting","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κραιπάλη</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kraipálē</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">krahee-pal'-ay</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Surfeiting</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"பாரமடைதல் - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"drunken dissipation, surfeiting; a headache"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Probably from the same as <a href=\"#/G726 - ἁρπάζω - harpázō - har-pad'-zo/726\">G726</a>; properly a <i>headache</i> (as a <i>seizure</i> of pain) from drunkenness, that is, (by implication) a <i>debauch</i> (by analogy a <i>glut</i>): - surfeiting.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}